{"4486840": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Perfect Son-In-Law: Hidden S-Rank", "steam_appid": 4486840, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>此商店頁面由人工智慧協助翻譯。如果本遊戲在華語社群中獲得足夠的關注與支持，正式版將提供專業製作的繁體中文翻譯。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/ce88dc685d8d15af1380babc0be9fb70.avif?t=1776079250\" width=1280 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/b22b06ecfa26a1dabdb35c4ef846199c.poster.avif?t=1776079250\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/b22b06ecfa26a1dabdb35c4ef846199c.webm?t=1776079250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/b22b06ecfa26a1dabdb35c4ef846199c.mp4?t=1776079250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兩年前，地城開始出現在世界各地。每當新的地城誕生時，總會有一些人被隨機拖入其中。生還率極低。能夠活著出來的人，往往早已不再是原來的自己。除了創傷之外，他們也變得更強——因為在地城中擊殺怪物能帶來力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，有些人獲得的遠不止如此。他們被稱為Awakeners。藉由在地城中發現的魔法神器，他們能解鎖各種超自然技能與能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但即使在Awakeners之中，你的情況也顯得格外異常。許多人都提到過會顯示能力數值的紫色狀態介面……卻從沒有人說過，它還可能變成黑色……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/640245ee6b9b5d30bf2b5c3c725321e5.avif?t=1776079250\" width=1280 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/96ef888b97c2563162def9c4c5075632.poster.avif?t=1776079250\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/96ef888b97c2563162def9c4c5075632.webm?t=1776079250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/96ef888b97c2563162def9c4c5075632.mp4?t=1776079250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stacy Kirsch在家族拼命維持地位、不願走向沒落的局勢中成了犧牲品。不願再當棋盤上的一顆棋子，她決定反抗家族，徹底打亂他們替她安排婚姻的計畫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，就是那個攪局的人。即使你們才剛認識不久，她仍請求你在各種正式場合假扮她的男朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上流社會很快就會下定論。在一個充滿訂製西裝、家族聯盟與精心維持笑容的場合裡，像你這樣的人顯然格格不入。被偏見蒙蔽的多數人，很快就會把你當成無足輕重的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，並不是這個世界上的每個人都會用同樣的眼光看待你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/4eade23e90e26ec7fca805251a5e68d0.avif?t=1776079250\" width=1280 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/a214c1b1743a1a2f6057b9a0d7fa6067.poster.avif?t=1776079250\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/a214c1b1743a1a2f6057b9a0d7fa6067.webm?t=1776079250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4486840/extras/a214c1b1743a1a2f6057b9a0d7fa6067.mp4?t=1776079250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >假扮Stacy的男朋友，將你拉進一個充滿期待、野心與隱藏動機的世界。但你答應扮演的這個角色，也許並不是你真正想要的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著故事推進，新的連結開始出現。有些人看見了那個被他人忽視的你。有些人早已比任何人都更了解你。而有些人，則會在你最意想不到的時候出現。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的選擇將決定哪些關係會逐漸加深，哪些則始終無法觸及。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這款以劇情為核心的